# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ANAXION TECHNOLOGIES — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env.local to git.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── SITE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://anaxion.tech

# ── EMAILJS (Contact Form) ───────────────────────────────────────
# Setup steps:
#   1. Sign up free at https://emailjs.com
#   2. Add Email Service → connect Gmail or Outlook → copy Service ID
#   3. Create Email Template with these variables:
#        {{from_name}}  {{from_email}}  {{company}}
#        {{budget}}     {{service}}     {{message}}
#   4. Copy Template ID from template settings
#   5. Account → API Keys → copy Public Key
#
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=service_xxxxxxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=template_xxxxxxx
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ── UMAMI ANALYTICS (Free, GDPR-safe, no cookies) ────────────────
# Setup steps:
#   1. Sign up free at https://umami.is
#   2. Add Website → enter anaxion.tech
#   3. Copy the Website ID shown after creation
#   Free plan: 3 websites, 100k events/month
#
NEXT_PUBLIC_UMAMI_WEBSITE_ID=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

# ── GOOGLE ANALYTICS 4 (Optional — requires cookie consent) ──────
# Setup steps:
#   1. Sign up at https://analytics.google.com
#   2. Create GA4 property → copy Measurement ID (format: G-XXXXXXXXXX)
#   NOTE: GA4 is opt-in. Only loads if this variable is set.
#   NOTE: Requires cookie consent banner (already implemented).
#
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# ── NODE ENVIRONMENT ─────────────────────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development
